data.title: Zoe Salmon has gotten married in Barbados!
data.meta_description: The former Blue Peter presenter and Northern Irish star has tied the knot in a surprise wedding in Barbados. Bangor-born Zoe Salmon has wed her beau, William Corrie from Newtownards, by eloping to the tropical island of Barbados. The loved-up pair tied the knot at the exclusive five-star Sandy Lane resort- a favourite of Rihanna and Simon Cowell.
